These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, country
House: cape-cod, cottage
1. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
2. the cottage house is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | funk |
| House       | cape-cod | cottage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: peas, zucchini
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, spy
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
2. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Food   | peas | zucchini |
| Movie-Genre      | spy     | mystery  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, swisher
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Cigar   | vegafina | swisher  |
| Beverage   | milk | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
