1. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |
| Food   | garlic   | zucchini     |
| Birthday   | december | march |

